data.description: Beautiful estate in the gated community of Oaks of Buffalo Way. This homes features 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bath, 4 Living Room-Bonus areas, designated Office space, 4 Car Garage and so much more! The master bedroom is truly a sanctuary to behold, with plenty of space to unwind and soak away the worries of the day. Every corner of the property, with its vaulted ceilings and intricate detail, offers sophistication and class. This remarkable home sits on almost 1.5 acres, with plenty of mature trees, an incredible backyard with a beautiful pool, perfect for relaxing or entertaining!  This is the kind of home dreams are made of!
